city.cs.engine

Class SensorEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • city.cs.engine.SensorEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SensorEvent
extends EventObject
    Event object describing contact between a Sensor and a solid fixture. These events are reported at the beginning and end of the contact, to any listeners attached to the sensor.
    See Also:
